1) install luci-ssl (opkg install luci-ssl) or related
2) create the certdrop user and directory (./certdrop_user.sh)
3) restart dropbear (/etc/init.d/dropbear restart)
4) sync the keys from remote host
5) edit /etc/confg/uhttpd to use the certificates from remote host
6) restart uhttpd (/etc/init.d/uhttpd restart)

